      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIGGER SURE CAN (2) was well fancied last time on the back of some sparkling form, which included a two-start winning streak, but could only manage second (25.24) at Maitland. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Rates highly and will give a great sight. CAWBOURNE OZZY (3) produced a powerful 19.74 winning over 350m at Goulburn last start. Harder here but expected to measure up. EUREKA MAC (1) finished fourth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 630m at Nowra, taking a Grade 5 in a sharp 36.42. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. TRALAERO (4) missed the frame latest (25.45) when fourth over 440m at Goulburn in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw.",
